{
  "texts": [
    "According to Dewey, intelligence participates in habit reconstruction through judgment, memory, reflection, and other abilities.",
    "Habit is \"an ability,…formed through past experience\" (Dewey, 2008b, p. 48), and adopting certain customs and experiences is akin to the process of supervised learning.",
    "Second, researchers employed a reinforcement learning framework resembling reward learning to further enhance ChatGPT's various capabilities (Schulman et al., 2017).",
    "A professional team ranked and labeled generated complex scenarios and diverse answers, then trained a reward model capable of scoring texts based on those labels.",
    "The reward model judged the effectiveness of ChatGPT and provided it with feedback to continue improving its abilities."
  ]
}